          <div class="service-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i>
          </div>
          <a href="green-orbit-digital.html" class="card-action d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded-circle">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-up-right"></i>
          </a>
          <h3>
            <a href="green-orbit-digital.html">
              Sustainable <span>Digital Strategy</span>
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p>
            Green Orbit Digital develops data-driven digital strategies, SEO, analytics, content systems, and low-carbon web solutions that drive measurable growth for space organisations and tech ventures.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Green Orbit Space Communications & PR -->
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="service-card position-relative z-1">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-megaphone"></i>
          </div>
          <a href="green-orbit-communications.html" class="card-action d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded-circle">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-up-right"></i>
          </a>
          <h3>
            <a href="green-orbit-communications.html">
              Communications <span>& PR</span>
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p>
            We craft mission-aligned messaging, stakeholder engagement, and narrative frameworks to help space organisations communicate complex technologies clearly, credibly, and impactfully.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Green Orbit Academy -->
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="service-card position-relative z-1">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-mortarboard-fill"></i>
          </div>
          <a href="green-orbit-academy.html" class="card-action d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded-circle">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-up-right"></i>
          </a>
          <h3>
            <a href="green-orbit-academy.html">
              Capability <span>Development & Training</span>
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p>
            Green Orbit Academy delivers workshops, leadership programmes, and bespoke training in sustainable marketing, digital transformation, impact frameworks, and space ecosystem development.
